swap

Operation

Swap the top two operands on the stack

Format

swap

Forms

swap = 43(0x2b)

Stack

..., value1, value2 => ..., value2, value1

Description

Swap the top two values on the stack. Pop value2 and value1. Push value2, then push value1.

Runtime exceptions

None.

Notes

None.
